# Kit review

**Prerequisite:** [VERIFICATION.md](../agent_dev_kit/docs/guidelines/VERIFICATION.md) must pass in a **separate agent session** before review.

Before commit or PR, follow [docs/guidelines/REVIEW.md](../agent_dev_kit/docs/guidelines/REVIEW.md):

1. Answer all four security questions on the diff.
2. Check spec conformance when `.ai/*-spec.md` exists.
3. Run DoD checklist from [registry/dod.yaml](../agent_dev_kit/registry/dod.yaml).
4. Use fixed review output format from REVIEW.md.
5. Wait for explicit developer approval before commit.

Defer to user TDD and semantic-commit rules when present.
